=== Noun ===
'''anti-semitism'''

# discrimination or hatred against [[jew]]s
# discrimination or hatred against [[semitic]] peoples ''(Literal interpretation; very rarerly used.)''

====Usage Note====
Because the term can be interpreted as ''extreme hatred to the point of [[genocide]]'', care should be taken when inferring it to people or organisations. If the interpretation is not clear from context, then substituting a more precise phrase may be advisable.

